lead_paragraph: Geno Auriemma didn't what kind of performance he'd get out of his UConn team Wednesday night, but he said the top-ranked Huskies played very well in routing Nebraska 84-41 to take their 86th consecutive victory.

headline.print_headline: Samuelson Scores 23 as No 1. UConn Rolls Over Nebraska 84-41
